This paper examines the impact of community identification on political interaction in Wikipedia, which involves social media analysis, network analysis, and community participation analysis. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), followed by cs.CY (Computers and Society), cs.SD (Software Engineering), cs.SOC (Social and Information Networks), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
